summary: Danariel StormBow, now for TBD, includes TBD Demon Hunter retextures too!
descriptionHtml: Pretty much a pet project to give me modding and modeling experience, this mod converts the famous Danariel Stormbow follower to the Touched By Dibella body type. It also includes a converted version of the Demon Hunter armor for the tbd body, includes two new holiday themed retextures.Â
